;Where can I buy Firefox OS?
我在哪裡能買到 Firefox OS 裝置？


;Firefox OS will be available to buy in July 2013 from Movistar stores in Spain, Venezuela and Colombia. You can also purchase through T-Mobile stores in Poland.
自 2013 年 7 月起，可在西班牙、委內瑞拉、哥倫比亞境內的 Movistar 商店購得 Firefox OS 裝置。波蘭境內的 T-Mobile 商店亦將推出。


;To date, 17 operators spanning the globe have committed to distributing Firefox OS devices: América Móvil, China Unicom, Deutsche Telekom, Etisalat, Hutchison Three Group, KDDI, KT, MegaFon, Qtel, SingTel, Smart, Sprint, Telecom Italia Group, Telefónica, Telenor, TMN and VimpelCom.
