;As a result, more countries and mobile phone operators will be selling Firefox OS; further news will be announced in the coming weeks. Our operator partners will distribute the phones through a variety of locally-specific channels.
所以會有越來越多國家與電信營運商推出 Firefox OS，而我們另將在數週之內發佈更多消息。與 Mozilla 合作的電信營運商，均會透過當地特定管道推出 Firefox OS 手機。


